Movement:
Pawns should be allowed to move 1 step forward              D
Pawns should not be allowed to move 2 steps forward         D
Pawns should not be allowed to move sideways                D
Pawns should not be allowed to move backwards               D
Pawns should not be allowed to move diagonally              D
Pawns should not be allowed to move to occupied fields      D

Rooks should be allowed to move up, down, left and right for multiple fields at one move
Rooks should not move diagonally
Rooks should not be allowed to jump over any pieces